name: JK Small Breasts Microbikini
description:
It's so small, but I still prefer without 😜

This is V01 version of updated Lora that you can see in my Patreon.
Preview of V02, with Full LoRA you gain consistency, smaller swimsuits, and big variation of poses.

To celebrate 69 patreons and 120 people on the discord server I announce the first prompt contest (on discord server) worth a LoRA exclusively yours!!!

LoRA prompt weight: 0.6 to 0.8
Model used for training: Uber Realistic Porn Merge 1.3.

Recomendations:

  • CFG ~9

  • Steps >=28

  • DPM Family or DDIM

Prompts that can improve your results: flat_chest, tiny_micro_bikini...

Tendencies of this LoRA (and resolution):

  • This model was made for slim girls, the results with curvy girls aren't good.

  • It's common the metallic effect on bikinis, you can put "matte", "velvet" or other finish on pos prompt.

  • Sometimes nipples can pop out of bikini, you can put "nipples" on neg.

  • Necklaces and navel piercings can appear, I liked them, but you can put "necklace" and "navel piercing" on neg if you don't want this.

See my other LoRAs:

  • Puffy Nipples

  • Perfect Perky Breasts

  • Tight Bikini Top

  • Small Breasts [Lite]

  • Big Natural Breasts Type01 [Lite]

  • Big Natural Breasts Type02 [Lite]

  • Ghost Nipples [Lite]

  • Underwater Naked Shot

  • Fake Breasts [Lite]

  • Macromastia [Lite]

  • Big Ass Slim Waist (PAWG ver.)

🐔
